author: codeblobsTV
description:
CodeblobsTV is a channel with curated video content for those of you whom are enthusiastic on how web technology stacks work, how things fit together and for those who are willing to dip their toes in unknown waters and learn new technologies, tools and technology stacks in an ever changing environment.

The goal of this channel is to provide a hands-on experience in the sense that almost all videos will be based in some real use case scenario which hopefully will help the audience start thinking critically of what to use when and most importantly why.
